title: Consensus Check — Funding a Political Defense of DeFi
body: Should governance allocate 1M UNI from the Community Treasury to fund a 501(c)(4) to defend the protocol and DeFi from legal and regulatory threats and help ensure the promise of DeFi?
author: 0x61c8D4e4BE6477Bb49791540Ff297Ef30Eaa01c2
